#: ../../source/janim/items/effect/frame_effect.rst:2
msgid "frame_effect"
msgstr "frame_effect"

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.FrameEffect:1 of
msgid "将传入的着色器 ``fragment_shader`` 应用到 ``items`` 上"
msgstr "Applies the passed shader ``fragment_shader`` to ``items``"

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.FrameEffect:3 of
msgid "着色器基本格式："
msgstr "Basic shader format:"

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.FrameEffect:5 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"#version 330 core\n"
"\n"
"in vec2 v_texcoord; // 传入的纹理坐标\n"
"out vec4 f_color;   // 输出的颜色\n"
"\n"
"uniform sampler2D fbo; // 传入的纹理（承载了 items 的渲染结果）\n"
"\n"
"#[JA_FINISH_UP_UNIFORMS]\n"
"\n"
"void main()\n"
"{\n"
"    // 进行处理，例如\n"
"    f_color = texture(fbo, v_texcoord); // 读取纹理颜色\n"
"    f_color.rgb = 1.0 - f_color.rgb; // 反色\n"
"\n"
"    #[JA_FINISH_UP]\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"#version 330 core\n"
"\n"
"in vec2 v_texcoord; // Input texture coordinates\n"
"out vec4 f_color;   // Output color\n"
"\n"
"uniform sampler2D fbo; // Input texture (containing the rendering results of items)\n"
"\n"
"#[JA_FINISH_UP_UNIFORMS]\n"
"\n"
"void main()\n"
"{\n"
"    // Perform processing, for example\n"
"    f_color = texture(fbo, v_texcoord); // Read texture color\n"
"    f_color.rgb = 1.0 - f_color.rgb; // Invert colors\n"
"\n"
"    #[JA_FINISH_UP]\n"
"}"

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.FrameEffect:25 of
msgid "其中 ``#[JA_FINISH_UP]`` 是一个占位符，JAnim 会在这里做一些额外的操作，前面的 ``#[JA_FINISH_UP_UNIFORMS]`` 与之对应"
msgstr ""
"``#[JA_FINISH_UP]`` is a placeholder where JAnim performs additional operations, and the preceding "
"``#[JA_FINISH_UP_UNIFORMS]`` corresponds to it"

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.FrameEffect:27 of
msgid "上述代码最核心的是 ``main`` 中“进行处理”的部分，其余的代码作为固定的写法照抄即可"
msgstr ""
"The core of the above code is the “processing” part in ``main``, the rest of the code can be copied as fixed patterns"

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.FrameEffect:29 of
msgid "如果懒得抄，可以用 :class:`SimpleFrameEffect`，这个类只要写“进行处理”这部分就好了，因为它把其余代码都封装了"
msgstr ""
"If you don't want to copy, you can use :class:`SimpleFrameEffect`, which only requires writing the “processing” part, as "
"it encapsulates the rest of the code"

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.FrameEffect:31 of
msgid "完整示例请参考 :ref:`基础样例 <basic_examples>` 中的对应代码"
msgstr "For complete examples, refer to the corresponding code in :ref:`Basic Examples <basic_examples>`"

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.FrameEffect.add:3 of
msgid "调用 :meth:`add` 很可能不会按预期工作"
msgstr "Calling :meth:`add` is unlikely to work as expected."

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.FrameEffect.add:5 of
msgid "如果你想应用额外的物件，需要使用 :meth:`apply`"
msgstr "If you want to apply additional items, use :meth:`apply`."

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.FrameEffect.remove:3 of
msgid "调用 :meth:`remove` 很可能不会按预期工作"
msgstr "Calling :meth:`remove` is unlikely to work as expected."

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.FrameEffect.remove:5 of
msgid "如果你想应用额外的物件，需要使用 :meth:`discard`"
msgstr "If you want to discard applied items, use :meth:`discard`."

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.FrameEffect.apply:1 of
msgid "对更多物件应用效果"
msgstr "Apply the effect to more items."

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.FrameEffect.discard:1 of
msgid "对指定物件的取消应用效果"
msgstr "Remove the effect from the specified items."

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.SimpleFrameEffect:1 of
msgid ":class:`FrameEffect` 的简化封装，具体请参考 :class:`FrameEffect` 中的说明"
msgstr "Simplified wrapper for :class:`FrameEffect`, for details refer to the description in :class:`FrameEffect`"

#: janim.items.effect.frame_effect.SimpleFrameEffect:5 of
msgid "如果该着色器代码中出现报错，会显示为 ``JA_SIMPLE_FRAMEEFFECT_SHADER`` 中出现的"
msgstr "If an error occurs in the shader code, it will be displayed as occurring in ``JA_SIMPLE_FRAMEEFFECT_SHADER``."
